com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims
Class UserInfoClaims

java.lang.Object
  com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims.JSONObjectClaims
      com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims.UserInfoClaims

public class UserInfoClaims
extends JSONObjectClaims

UserInfo claims, serialisable to a JSON object.

Example UserInfo claims set: 

 {
   "user_id"     : "248289761001",
   "name"        : "Jane Doe",
   "given_name"  : "Jane",
   "family_name" : "Doe",
   "email"       : "janedoe@example.com",
   "picture"     : "http://example.com/janedoe/me.jpg"
 }

See http://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-messages-1_0.html#anchor14

Version:
0.9 (2012-05-17)
Author:
Vladimir Dzhuvinov

putIntoJSONObject

protected static void putIntoJSONObject(net.minidev.json.JSONObject o,
                                        java.util.Map<com.nimbusds.langtag.LangTag,? extends StringClaimWithLangTag> claims)
Puts the speicifed string claims with optional language tags into a JSON object.

Example: 

 {
   "country"       : "USA",
   "country#en"    : "USA",
   "country#de_DE" : "Vereinigte Staaten",
   "country#fr_FR" : "Etats Unis"
 }

Parameters:
o - The JSON object. May be null.
claims - The claims. May be null.
